[normal] 15 amends section 52 of the RTA to extend the Secretary of State’s power to Authorise Premises as Test Facilities as testing stations for the purposes of roadworthiness testing to the testing of lorries. Or the whole ATF strategy will not be "Authorised? 395.
[normal]PCS is concerned that if the charging process is simplified, the ATFs will be able to take the monies and pay direct to a central body, bypassing VOSA staff checks, which may result in job losses for administrative grades.
